<h2>You have a new Cross Selling List waiting for you!</h2>

<p><%= @publisher.name %> has shared the cross selling list '<%= @cross_selling_list.name %>' with you.</p>

<p>To subscribe to this list and set any or all of the products live in your catalog,</p>

<div class="lo_call_to_action">
  <%= link_to "Review List", admin_market_cross_selling_list_url(@subscriber, @cross_selling_list, host: (@subscriber ? @subscriber.domain : "app.#{Figaro.env.domain}")), class: "lo_button lo_button_large" %>
